        "detail": "201 discountable samples in the 2012-2015 windows of near-cutoff sites; 35 of 87 near-cutoff sites reconstructed. Re-including them shifts the running variable by at most 0.350 log10 and flips Poor/Sufficient status for 9 site(s). Re-estimated effect 0.0121 vs baseline -0.0272 (delta 0.0394, within 1.96*baseline sd 0.3325 = true). mean |kept-only minus official| margin = 0.038 over 35 sites (method-fidelity check)."
      }
